title: ABBYY PDF Transformer+ 12.0.104.799 Multilingual Full With Medic
description:
[img]http://babupc.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ABBYY-PDF-Transformer.gif[/img]

ABBYY PDF Transformer+

ABBYY PDF Transformer+ is an easy-to-use, versatile tool that lets you create, edit, comment on, and convert PDF files to other editable formats such as DOCX and XLSX. ABBYY PDF Transformer+ can convert paper documents to searchable PDF files, merge files of various formats into a single PDF document, add or remove pages from a document and change their order, or edit text and copy pictures and text from PDF files to other applications, all without the need to convert PDF documents to an editable format. ABBYY PDF Transformer+ also has a number of features for commenting, discussing documents, and creating document archives. ABBYY PDF Transformer+ can convert PDF documents to two popular ebook formats: EPUB and FB2. You can read these ebooks on your iPad, tablet, or other mobile device.
Features:

    Work with any type of PDF
    Enjoy intuitive navigation
    Convert to editable formats
    Extract and quote text
    Benefit from comprehensive language support
    Scan to searchable PDF
    Create PDF
    Create one PDF file from multiple files
    Comment and annotate
    and many many more….

What’s New in ABBYY PDF Transformer+ 12
